OL,4,CBank of Mum and Dad 'feels the pinch'
OL,5, Parents are parting with thousands of
OL,6, pounds to help their children get on
OL,7, the property ladder, but they can't
OL,8, afford to lend as much as they used to.
OL,10,FThe average parental contribution for
OL,11,Fhome buyers this year will be B#18,000,
OL,12,Fdown 17% from last year's B#21,600,
OL,13,Faccording to Legal & General (L&G).
OL,15,FThe drop shows that parents are
OL,16,F"feeling the pinch", the firm says.
OL,18,FNonetheless, more than one in four
OL,19,Fbuyers are still expected to receive
OL,20,Ffinancial help from friends or family.
